A decorator wrapper for {class}`ServerMainContextManager`

Usage example:

```python
@aiotools.main
def mymain():
    server_args = do_init()
    stop_sig = yield server_args
    if stop_sig == signal.SIGINT:
        do_graceful_shutdown()
    else:
        do_forced_shutdown()

aiotools.start_server(..., main_ctxmgr=mymain, ...)
```
